#: server.py:15
msgid "CVE修复流程自动化工具，提供CVE分析、补丁适配等功能"
msgstr ""
"CVE remediation process automation tool, providing CVE analysis, patch "
"adaptation, and other functions"

#: server.py:19 server.py:258
msgid "Gitee访问令牌"
msgstr "Gitee access token"

#: server.py:23
msgid "执行cvekit命令并返回结果"
msgstr "execute cvekit command line and return result"

#: server.py:86
#, python-format
msgid "cvekit执行失败: %s"
msgstr "execute cvekit failed: %s"

#: server.py:89
msgid "cvekit输出非JSON格式"
msgstr "cvekit outputs in non-JSON format"

#: server.py:93
msgid ""
"\n"
"    该函数是CVE修复流程的第一步：\n"
"        通过调用gitee的api，解析gitee issue URL并获取基本信息\n"
"        在这里将通过issue_url解析得到的issue_info以json格式反馈给用户\n"
"        主要告知用户我们获取的issue_id, cve_id, org_name, repo_name, "
"affected_versions这些是否正确，需要用户确认\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"   This function is the first step in the CVE remediation process:\n"
"       By calling the API of Gitee, parse the Gitee issue URL and obtain "
"basic information.\n"
"       Here, the issue_info parsed from the issue_url will be fed back to"
" the user in JSON format.\n"
"       The main purpose is to inform the user of the issue_id, cve_id, "
"org_name, repo_name that we have obtained.\n"
"       Whether these affected_versions are correct needs to be confirmed "
"by the user.\n"
"   "

