#: server.py:122
msgid ""
"\n"
"    该函数是CVE修复流程的第二步：\n"
"        设置仓库环境，克隆官方仓库，添加fork远程\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"   This function is the second step in the CVE remediation process:\n"
"       Set up the repository environment, clone the official repository, "
"and add a fork as a remote\n"
"   "

