msgstr "The repository has been downloaded to %s"

#: server.py:141
msgid ""
"\n"
"    该函数是CVE修复流程的第三步：\n"
"        获取漏洞相关的真实上游提交信息，并将获取到的commit告知给用户\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"   This function is the third step in the CVE remediation process:       "
"Obtain the actual upstream commit information related to the "
"vulnerability, and notify the user of the obtained commit.   "

#: server.py:156
#, python-format
msgid "获取提交信息失败: %s"
msgstr "Failed to obtain submission information: %s"

#: server.py:158
#, python-format
msgid "已获取CVE %s的提交信息:\n"
msgstr "Commit information for CVE %s has been obtained:\n"

#: server.py:159
#, python-format
msgid "- 引入漏洞的提交: %s\n"
msgstr "- Submission of introduced vulnerabilities: %s\n"

#: server.py:160
#, python-format
msgid "- 修复漏洞的提交: %s\n"
msgstr "- Submission of vulnerability fixes: %s\n"

#: server.py:161
msgid "请确认以上提交信息是否正确"
msgstr "Please confirm whether the above information is correct"

#: server.py:165
msgid ""
"\n"
"    该函数是CVE修复流程的第四步：\n"
"        分析introduced_commit在本地仓库的哪些分支被引入，如果引入的话，是否被fixed了，以此来分析哪些分支需要应用补丁"
"\n"
"        并检查从上游获取的补丁直接应用，是否存在冲突\n"
"        "
"该步骤中的参数branches为kernel的分支名，和issue分析中的受影响版本并不一致，若用户未输入要分析的分支名，使用默认值即可\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"   This function is the fourth step in the CVE remediation process:\n"
"       Analyze which branches of the local repository the "
"introduced_commit has been introduced to, and if so, whether it has been "
"fixed, in order to determine which branches require patch application.\n"
"       And check whether there are conflicts when directly applying the "
"patches obtained from upstream.\n"
"       The parameter 'branches' in this step refers to the branch name of"
" the kernel, which is not consistent with the affected version in the "
"issue analysis. If the user does not input the branch name to be "
"analyzed, the default value can be used.\n"
"    "

#: server.py:173
msgid "要分析的分支列表，逗号分隔"
msgstr "The list of branches to be analyzed, separated by commas"

