"\n"
msgstr ""
"Branch analysis completed, with %d affected branches identified:\n"
"\n"

#: server.py:209
msgid "请确认以上分析结果"
msgstr "Please confirm the above analysis results"

#: server.py:213
msgid ""
"\n"
"    该函数是CVE修复流程的第五步：\n"
"        对于第四步中分析出的受影响分支，分别应用相对应的patch，参数中的patch_path为第四步的冲突点\n"
"        若patch应用成功，提交之后，把该分支推送到fork仓，若patch应用失败，尝试解决冲突后，重新执行该步骤\n"
"        本地代码位于工作空间里面的仓库名所在的目录\n"
"        若没有受影响分支，该步骤可跳过\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"   This function is the fifth step in the CVE remediation process:\n"
"       For the affected branches identified in step 4, apply the "
"corresponding patches respectively. The patch_path in the parameters "
"refers to the conflict point in step 4.\n"
"       If the patch application is successful, after submitting, push the"
" branch to the fork repository. If the patch application fails, try to "
"resolve the conflicts and then re-execute this step.\n"
"       The local code is located in the directory corresponding to the "
"repository name in the workspace\n"
"       If there are no affected branches, this step can be skipped\n"
"   "

#: server.py:222
msgid "要应用patch的分支名"
msgstr "The branch name to apply the patch"

#: server.py:223 server.py:254
msgid "fork仓库url"
msgstr "Fork repository URL"

#: server.py:224
msgid "patch路径"
msgstr "Patch file path"

#: server.py:240
#, python-format
msgid "应用patch失败: %s"
msgstr "Failed to apply patch: %s"

#: server.py:242
#, python-format
msgid "patch应用成功, 目标分支: %s, 修复分支: %s, patch: %s"
msgstr "Apply patch successful, target branch: %s, fix branch: %s, patch: %s"

#: server.py:245
msgid ""
"\n"
"    该函数是CVE修复流程的第六步：\n"
"        对于第五步中修复成功的分支，提交pr，若用户未提供目标仓库url，则使用默认的目标仓库\n"
"        若所有分支均已修复，该步骤可跳过\n"
"        参数中的branch是受影响分支名，提交pr的目标分支\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"   This function is the sixth step in the CVE remediation process:\n"
"       For the branch successfully fixed in step 5, submit a pull request"
" (PR). If the user does not provide a target repository URL, the default "
"target repository will be used.\n"
"        If all branches have been repaired, this step can be skipped\n"
"        The \"branch\" parameter refers to the name of the affected "
"branch, which is the target branch for submitting the pull request (PR)\n"
"   "

